overview:
Nohel Corral founded and managed CollegeToCareers.com, an educational portal designed to connect students and professionals with scholarships, grants, and continued educational opportunities. Nohel currently serves as an administrator at a California community college using his educational background to network with organizations and students creating a dynamic online educational community.

With more than five years of experience in creating, marketing, and selling online properties, Nohel uses his strong foundation of Search Engine Optimization (SEO) to help sites generate traffic organically.

degrees.subject: Counseling, Specialization in Student Development in Higher Education
